{"tid":970143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基因改造突破 農產量增四成 提升光合作用效率 可解糧食危機","createTime":"2019-01-05T14:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T16:39:43.000Z","uid":229553,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dee2b8f7230126945739ba1bd5a57170ec49aaf8","tid":970143,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"希望唔洗到 要食昆蟲蛋白質既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國科學家透過基因改造提高植物光合作用效率，令農作物增產四成，有望促成新一代農業革命。美國伊利諾伊州大學及美國農業研究局在《科學》刊登實驗成果，稱經基因改造煙草比一般煙草增產四成，今年將應用同樣技術在馬鈴薯上，這次歷時兩年的實驗在真實環境進行。研究人員稱希望有關研究可助紓解世界糧食危機，但承認基因改造有爭議，新技術要安全應用於糧食生產還需要進一步評估及研究，估計最少要10年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190105/s00014/1546625905329/%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4-%E8%BE%B2%E7%94%A2%E9%87%8F%E5%A2%9E%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E5%85%89%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87-%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%A3%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190105%2Fs00014%2F1546625905329%2F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2580%25A0%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A0%25B4-%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%258D%2587%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%258E%2587-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E7%25B3%25A7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F&d=bXOg%2FiaxOvVhA0i%2Fv%2FEqqpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=55efd639\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190105%2Fs00014%2F1546625905329%2F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2580%25A0%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A0%25B4-%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%25